			<div class="mk-grid">
		
			
<div style="" class="vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column column_container  _ height-full">
	
<h1 id="fancy-title-9" class="mk-fancy-title  simple-style  color-single">
	<span>
				WORKING WITH PETROTECHNICS.			</span>
</h1>
<div class="clearboth"></div>



</div>
		
		</div>	
	</div>


	<div class="mk-main-wrapper-holder">
		<div class="theme-page-wrapper full-layout mk-grid vc_row-fluid no-padding">
			<div class="theme-content no-padding">

				</div></div></div>
	

<div class="wpb_row vc_row  mk-fullwidth-true  attched-false    vc_custom_1474051653603 vc_row-fluid  js-master-row ">
			<div class="mk-grid">
		
			
<div style="" class="vc_col-sm-2 wpb_column column_container  _ height-full">
	</div>

<div style="" class="vc_col-sm-8 wpb_column column_container  _ height-full">
	
<div id="text-block-10" class="mk-text-block   ">

	
	<p style="text-align: center; color: #fff;">From the beginning, we had a single-minded purpose: to keep people safe in hazardous industries. When Phil Murray founded this Company in 1989, he passionately believed that innovative technology-based solutions would reduce operational risk. This belief informs our whole culture. And to us, thats the most important thing driving our business.</p>
<p style="text-align: center; color: #fff;">&#8220;Culture eats strategy for breakfast.&#8221;<br />
&#8211; Peter Drucker (business guru).</p>

	<div class="clearboth"></div>
</div>
</div>

<div style="" class="vc_col-sm-2 wpb_column column_container  _ height-full">
	</div>
		
		</div>	
	</div>


	<div class="mk-main-wrapper-holder">
		<div class="theme-page-wrapper full-layout mk-grid vc_row-fluid no-padding">
			<div class="theme-content no-padding">

				</div></div></div>
	

<div class="wpb_row vc_row  mk-fullwidth-true  attched-false    vc_row-fluid  js-master-row ">
		
			
<div style="" class="vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column column_container  _ height-full">
	
	<div class="wpb_single_image wpb_content_element vc_align_center  vc_custom_1474782192834  wistia_embed wistia_async_9gs08fgt7b popover=true popoverContent=link">
		
		<figure class="wpb_wrapper vc_figure">
			<a href="#" target="_self" class="vc_single_image-wrapper   vc_box_border_grey"><img width="1920" height="425" src="http://www.petrotechnics.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/video-bg.png" class="vc_single_image-img attachment-full" alt="video-bg" srcset="http://www.petrotechnics.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/video-bg.png 1920w, http://www.petrotechnics.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/video-bg-300x66.png 300w, http://www.petrotechnics.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/video-bg-768x170.png 768w, http://www.petrotechnics.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/video-bg-1024x227.png 1024w, http://www.petrotechnics.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/video-bg-330x73.png 330w, http://www.petrotechnics.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/video-bg-736x163.png 736w, http://www.petrotechnics.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/video-bg-1280x283.png 1280w, http://www.petrotechnics.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/video-bg-414x92.png 414w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></a>
