	<span class="mk-testimonial-author"></span></li><li class=" testimonial-item">
	<div class="mk-testimonial-content">
		<p class="mk-testimonial-quote"><blockquote>Process Safety Management is now connected to its impact on operations  so everyone can make better operational decisions.</blockquote></p>	</div>
	<span class="mk-testimonial-author"></span></li><li class=" testimonial-item">
	<div class="mk-testimonial-content">
		<p class="mk-testimonial-quote"><blockquote>Better operational decisions are creating measurable efficiencies  and improving my leading risk indicators.</blockquote></p>	</div>
	<span class="mk-testimonial-author"></span></li><li class=" testimonial-item">
	<div class="mk-testimonial-content">
		<p class="mk-testimonial-quote"><p style="color: #ffffff;"><em>"Process safety became part of the vernacular of the energy business However, it has also led to a reduction in responsibility and understanding of operational risk by operations staff In other words, operational risk has come to mean process safety and has been separated from operational performance as a whole, with the former managed by safety professionals and the latter by operational professionals."</em></p></p>	</div>
	<span class="mk-testimonial-author"></span></li>	</ul>
